## ğŸ› ï¸ Installation

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/yt-thumbnail-ranker.git
   cd yt-thumbnail-ranker
   ```

2. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```

3. Start the server:
   ```bash
   node server.js
   ```

4. Open your browser at:
   ```
   http://localhost:3000
   ```

